g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a652e5f8ad8fa622961ec512953ea9e3c04e89","tid":2247271,"uid":134103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8f0d03d02cf1c888e5d4cf94de0187b655a72b8","tid":2247271,"uid":379948,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac532f6f73633b824e68cf4d384306f5255b3919","tid":2247271,"uid":377401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"同你好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得自己不配被愛<br />\n以前拍過下散拖<br />\n覺得人哋對自己太好就開始疏遠人，覺得自己憑啲咩有人愛<br />\n身邊嘅朋友成日同自己講自己係值得有人中意值得被愛但自己真係覺得自己係個好差嘅人 覺得自己無嘢好 無自信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"睇你個名都知你好努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絲打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3c1a77f7e677e9bf516f85e0436a70c0c50a9d","tid":2247271,"uid":64884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"死咗去囉"},{"pid":"db22bb8a58be0d160b1c300becc242a8fe69795b","tid":2247271,"uid":307085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都會覺得人地鬧其他人 都係鬧緊自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c419e01f0b8619a1cd44af16a1876a7aab4cc263","tid":2247271,"uid":320680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"我由細到大對自己都冇信心，我做咩屋企人都覺得我唔會做得好、睇死我<br />\n有時有啲野我做唔到根本唔關我事，我根本控制唔到，但係佢哋係唔會理，係佢哋眼中我係垃圾，而家慢慢學識唔好理佢哋點諗，做好自己就算"},{"pid":"5ea94d09036283a1076103421184b5fa56883c62","tid":2247271,"uid":65268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T17:58:49.000Z","msg":"女仔都好啲肯講都會有人關心下<br />\n男一講隨時兜頭俾人屌到啪啪聲返被竇<br />\n即係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif